Binary file formats contain a 
    Header
    Body

Header for a bitmap contains 
    Identifier
        2 Bytes 
        BM on Win 3 and up
    Size
        4 Bytes
        up to ~34.36 Gigabytes

Lets do 
    200 x 200 white image
    300 x 200 black image
    300 x 50 gray image 


